channel.title: Java Slowness
channel.description: So on my webclient, at the begging, there is this java icon and it like goes around.. and it is loading, it goes insanely slow.. and I want to know how to fix it. How can I fix it? Is it my cache? or my client? and which one of these should I change it to my IP? [IMG]http://img14.imageshack.us/img14/2194/help123.jpg[/img]
